[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0459","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0459.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0273","title":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 Telnet 控制字符拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 Telnet 服务存在控制字符处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统的 telnet 端口发送 ^D（Ctrl+D）控制字符，导致 telnet 守护进程崩溃或进入异常状态，从而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，攻击利用难度低，无需特殊权限即可触发，属于典型的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0273"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.973","remediation":"升级至 Oracle Solaris 11 或更高版本，并停止使用 telnet 服务；在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行（或执行 svcadm disable telnet），改用 SSH 作为远程管理协议。若必须运行旧版系统，限制 telnet 服务的源 IP 访问并部署入侵检测规则监控异常 ^D 字符序列。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0273","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0273","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0273.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sunkill.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82086/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0459.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0424","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0239","title":"Netscape FastTrack Server 目录列表信息泄露漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 存在目录列表漏洞，由于服务器对 HTTP 方法的大小写处理不当，攻击者使用小写的 \"get\" 命令替代标准的大写 \"GET\" 发送请求时，服务器会返回根目录及子目录的文件列表，导致敏感信息泄露。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞遍历服务器文件系统，获取配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0239"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.770","remediation":"Netscape FastTrack Server 3.0.1 已停止维护超过二十年，官方不再提供安全补丁。建议立即迁移至仍受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 Microsoft IIS）。若短期内无法迁移，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面配置规则拦截小写 HTTP 方法（将小写 get 请求转换为 400/403 响应）作为临时缓解措施，同时严格限制可访问该服务器的源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/122","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1731","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19363","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0239","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0239.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0239.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74/GHSA-vcjq-7hcj-xh74.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netscape_fasttrack.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0424.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0424.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0257","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0114","title":"Elm elm-2.4 邮件系统本地符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Elm-2.4 邮件客户端中的 filter 命令存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 filter 命令以其他用户的权限执行任意命令或读取敏感文件。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户权限，影响范围包括使用 Elm-2.4 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或禁用 filter 功能。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0114"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.097","remediation":"立即升级至 Elm 2.4 Patch Level 3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令在处理临时文件时的竞态条件问题。若无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或移除 elm 的 setuid 权限位以限制 symlink 攻击。长期建议迁移至 mutt 或 alpine 等持续维护的邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0114"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0242","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0107","title":"Apache HTTP Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache 1.2.5 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量包含大量 `/` 字符的恶意 GET 请求触发此漏洞，导致 Apache 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Apache 1.2.5 及之前所有版本，攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0107"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.150","remediation":"建议升级至 Apache 1.3.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超大 GET 请求导致的缓冲区溢出。如无法升级，可在反向代理层（如 Nginx）限制单个 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节，并在 Web 应用防火墙中配置请求速率限制以缓解 DDoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0107","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20558","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0107","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0107.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0053","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0015","title":"Microsoft Windows TCP Teardrop 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Teardrop（泪滴）攻击是一种IP分片重组拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者通过向目标系统发送精心构造的、分片偏移量存在重叠的恶意IP数据包，导致目标系统在重组分片时触发内存计算错误，进而造成系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows 95/NT 3.51/NT 4.0 及 HP-UX 10.34 等操作系统，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，但需能够向目标发送IP数据包。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0015"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.280","remediation":"立即安装微软 MS98-001 安全更新（KB168747）以修复 TCP/IP 分片重组缺陷；对于已停止支持的 Windows 95/NT 4.0，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本；可在网络边界防火墙配置规则丢弃异常偏移的 IP 分片包作为临时缓解措施。针对 HP-UX 10.34，请升级至 HP-UX 11.0 以上版本或安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5579","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19103"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0048","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0015","title":"Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 分片重组拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Teardrop 拒绝服务漏洞利用 IP 分片重组机制的缺陷，攻击者向目标系统发送含有重叠偏移量的特制 IP 分片数据包，导致系统在重组时发生内存损坏而崩溃或重启。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.34、Windows 95/NT 3.5.1/NT 4.0 及后续 Service Pack 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，造成目标服务中断。此漏洞为早期经典的 DoS 攻击类型，已被公开的利用代码广泛使用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0015"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.280","remediation":"对于 Windows 95/NT 4.0 及更早版本，该漏洞官方补丁已停止支持，最终修复方案是升级到 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。对于 HP-UX 10.34，应升级到 HP-UX 11i v3 并安装最新补丁包。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上配置 ACL 规则丢弃非法 IP 分片包（如碎片偏移量重叠的数据包），并在受影响主机上禁用非必要的网络服务以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5579","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19103","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0015","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0015.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xj3h-gcxj-7pw6/GHSA-xj3h-gcxj-7pw6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/franckferman/Floodles/blob/144ec41e2f9052ac35701c26fe9e1fb081c44ef6/modules/ip_frag.py","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/T/teardrop.nasl","https://github.com/brevityinmotion/straylight/blob/3a51188edc3c08c6801402d81188f060cccd8d03/notebooks/Detectify-Learning.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0415","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0415.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0230","title":"Cisco 7xx 路由器 Telnet 服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 telnet 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备的 telnet 端口发送特制的超长请求，触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0230"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.653","remediation":"升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 IOS 至不受 1999 年 telnet 缓冲区溢出漏洞影响的版本（如 11.3 以上），或在全局配置模式下使用 `access-class` 限制 telnet 访问源地址，或禁用 telnet 服务改用 SSH 协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1102","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0230","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0230.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9hrh-6m37-36f5/GHSA-9hrh-6m37-36f5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0415.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0063","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0063.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0017","title":"Caldera OpenLinux FTP PORT 命令远程端口转发漏洞","description":"FTP 协议存在 FTP 反弹（FTP Bounce）漏洞，攻击者可通过 FTP 客户端的 PORT 命令指示 FTP 服务器向任意第三方主机的任意端口发起连接，从而利用该 FTP 服务器作为跳板绕过网络访问控制，实现对内网或其他受限网络的端口扫描与间接攻击。该漏洞影响多数支持主动模式（PORT 命令）的 FTP 服务器软件，攻击条件低，仅需能够与 FTP 服务器建立控制连接。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0017"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.560","remediation":"升级 FTP 服务器软件至支持 PORT 命令限制的版本（如 wu-ftpd 2.6.1+、vsftpd 2.0.1+），并启用第三方地址连接检查功能；在防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务器主动发起的出站连接，仅允许到客户端 IP 的 1024 以上端口；配置 FTP 服务端禁止 PORT 命令指向非客户端 IP 地址。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0017"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0063.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0059","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0018","title":"IBM AIX、SCO Unixware、SGI IRIX、Sun Solaris statd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"statd 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制 RPC 请求，触发 statd 守护进程中的缓冲区溢出，进而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2/4.1、SCO Unixware 7.1.1、SGI IRIX 5.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等多款 Unix 操作系统，利用方式为网络远程攻击，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0018"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.700","remediation":"立即安装各厂商提供的 rpc.statd 补丁包：Sun Solaris 2.5.1 安装 Sun 补丁 ID 105402-02 或更新版本；IBM AIX 4.1 安装 APAR IX64628；SGI IRIX 5.3 安装 SGI 安全补丁 19970801-01-P。如系统已停止维护，应升级到受支持的操作系统版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上禁止外部访问 portmap（TCP/UDP 111）和 rpc.statd 使用的动态端口（通常为 32771/4045），或停止 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/rpc.statd stop`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/127","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19104","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0018","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/rpc_statd.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0559","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0340","title":"Slackware Linux crond 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 系统中 crond 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 crond 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞允许拥有本地账户的攻击者利用 crond 在处理参数时的内存边界校验缺陷，实现权限提升。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Slackware Linux 系统。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制本地用户对 crond 的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0340"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.243","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 至 3.4 及以上版本，该修复版本已修正 crond 程序在处理用户提交的计划任务参数时的边界检查缺陷，防止本地用户通过特制参数触发缓冲区溢出提权。如无法升级，可限制 crond 仅允许受信用户通过 `cron.allow` 文件控制访问，并移除 `/etc/cron.d` 中不必要的任务文件。同时检查 crond 二进制是否被替换，使用 `rpm -V` 或 `md5sum` 校验文件完整性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0340"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0429","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0244","title":"Livingston RADIUS 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Livingston RADIUS 实现存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 RADIUS 认证服务发送特制数据包触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多个 Livingston 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或部署访问控制列表限制 RADIUS 服务访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0244"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.367","remediation":"立即升级 Livingston RADIUS 至 2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 RADIUS 代码中的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于无法升级的旧系统，应在边界防火墙上限制对 RADIUS UDP 端口 1812/1645 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 NAS 设备 IP 接入。建议迁移至当前仍受支持的 RADIUS 实现（如 FreeRADIUS 3.x），并在运行 RADIUS 服务的主机上启用栈缓冲区溢出保护机制（如 ASLR、NX）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4912a395-3fc6-4764-84b7-7d315af3698f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0376","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0193","title":"3Com 路由器 TCP 零长选项拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ascend 与 3Com 路由器在处理特殊构造的 TCP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标路由器发送包含零长度 TCP 选项（Zero Length TCP Option）的恶意数据包，触发设备处理异常导致路由器强制重启或崩溃。该漏洞影响 Ascend R 4.5 Ci12 及部分 3Com 路由器版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0193"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:52.973","remediation":"建议升级 Ascend Router 固件至 4.5 Ci12 之后的修复版本，或升级 3Com 路由器至厂商发布的修补固件。若暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙配置规则丢弃 TCP 选项长度为 0 的异常数据包，同时启用 TCP 状态检测功能缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0193","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20332","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0193","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0193.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000239.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0396","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0396.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0210","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris automountd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 系统中的自动挂载守护进程 automountd 存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，本地或远程攻击者可通过向 automountd 传递包含特殊 shell 字符的恶意请求，诱使系统以提升的权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可触发利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0210"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.103","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方补丁：Solaris 2.5.1 SPARC 平台安装 103613-01 或更新版本，x86 平台安装 103612-01 或更新版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装对应内核补丁。如无法立即升级，可在 `/etc/init.d/autofs` 中停止 automountd 服务并禁用自启动（`/etc/init.d/autofs stop; rm /etc/rc3.d/S74autofs`），同时在 `/etc/hosts.equiv` 和 `netgroup` 中限制可访问 automount 资源的主机范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88053459921223&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://www.cert.org/