"aliases":["CVE-1999-0021"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.013","remediation":"升级 wwwcount 至 2.4 及以上版本，或从 CGI 目录移除 Count.cgi 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面添加输入过滤规则，限制对 Count.cgi 的参数长度（如 Apache ModSecurity 限制 QUERY_STRING 不超过 256 字节），并确保以最低权限运行 CGI 程序。同时可在 Web 服务器访问控制中限制 Count.cgi 仅允许信任的来源 IP 调用，降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/128","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19105","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0021","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0021.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/count_cgi.nasl","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1149.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0511","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0306","title":"HP Xlock 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可构造特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖进程内存空间以执行任意代码，最终获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、HP-UX、IBM AIX、SGI IRIX、Solaris 等多个 Unix 系统的 xlock 程序，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞进行权限提升。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0306"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.993","remediation":"建议升级 xlock 至 2.5 以上版本，或安装对应操作系统厂商的补丁（HP-UX 11.00 及以上版本已修复此问题）。如无法升级，可限制 xlock 的 SUID 权限或改用其他屏幕锁定程序（如 xscreensaver、vlock）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0306","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19172"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml"}]